#

Lemon Zest Pork Parmesan with Hearty Tomato-Basil Meat Sauce

$18.5
600 kcal
Difficulty: 60%

Allergens:

DairyPork

Dietary Tags:

High ProteinLow Carb

Tags:

GourmetSavoryItalian Inspired

Description

A delightful fusion of zesty lemon and savory pork, topped with a rich tomato-basil sauce for a gourmet experience.

Ingredients

  • Pork loin: 1 lb
  • Parmesan cheese: 1 cup, grated
  • Lemon zest: 2 tablespoons
  • Olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • Garlic cloves: 3, minced
  • Canned crushed tomatoes: 28 oz
  • Fresh basil leaves: 1/4 cup, chopped
  • Salt: to taste
  • Black pepper: to taste
  • Red pepper flakes: 1 teaspoon (optional)
